					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1870235#post-2622666</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1870235/scp-2974#post-2622666</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 15 Sep 2016 12:33:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>SpectralDragon</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1558329</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I didn't even think of that skip while writing this one. I got the idea from a story about my mom finding a dried and salted lizard in her trail mix. The premise started out as simply &quot;Hey, what if the lizard had been alive?&quot;</p> <p>But I'm not quite sure I understand your point? 2186 is neither a fence lizard nor a zombie. 2974 has no abilities of environmental transformation, nor is it a chameleon. The only common point is that they're both lizards with strict care requirements. Would you mind explaining this to me a little more?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
