				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><sub>fence lizaaaaarrrdddddd ;~;</sub></p> <p>Context for anyone who wasn't in chat when this article was being reviewed: one time I found a lizard in my yard when it was time to clean up the storage junk piled up there. The lizard had been probably living in a box for some time so I felt bad for him and went to get some watermelon on a toothpick. The lizard just sat on the wall and I held out the watermelon and he just looked at it and licked it a few times and we were FRIENDS!!1!11!! then my mom walked over and the lizard disappeared into the bushes so I just left the watermelon on the wall. ;(</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
